<br />
<br />The only games I have problems with are Zelda (1) and Life Force, and I can't get my carts to boot on any other NES's either. However, I can pop in Dragon Warrior or Final Fantasy, play for a bit, and not worry about the Blow Dance wiping out my saves.
<br />
<br />Rob Nelson

		

